@baseUrl = http://localhost:5050

### Create a new order
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productName": "Widget Pro",
  "quantity": 5,
  "unitPrice": 29.99,
  "customerEmail": "customer@example.com"
}

### Create another order (Electronics)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productName": "Premium Headphones",
  "quantity": 2,
  "unitPrice": 199.99,
  "customerEmail": "john.doe@example.com"
}

### Create bulk order
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productName": "Office Supplies Pack",
  "quantity": 100,
  "unitPrice": 15.50,
  "customerEmail": "procurement@company.com"
}

### Health check (controller endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/health

### Health check (app health endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
